The quest command displays quest-related information.

Usage:
 quest list
 quest list all
 quest info <NUM>
 quest reset <NUM>

Available sub-commands:

    [color=blue]list[/color]: displays quests you are currently doing
    [color=blue]list all[/color]: displays quests you completed
    [color=blue]info[/color]: displays information about the specified (by number) quest
    [color=blue]reset[/color]: reset progress on the given quest
